{
 "name": "RPlog_Troy_and_Joir",
 "title": "Troy and Joir: Track Talk and Imperial Rumors",
 "summary": "At the Black Krayt Swoop Arena, the cold Imperial sponsor Joir seeks out the affable champion swoop racer Troy McTavish, who teasingly hints at explosive military scuttlebutt: Caspar has gone on alert, bracing for a possible civil war and an attack by a rebellious faction within the Empire. Troy withholds his proof, saving it for the Admiral who pays better, leaving Joir visibly rattled despite his trained composure. The two retire to Troy's immaculate repair shop, where his new assistant Azya serves coffee, and the racer Ellie Tracer and her brother Dak arrive to discuss putting an FLS swoop on hold. Amid banter about teams, sponsors, and bets, Troy and Joir wager a bottle of whiskey on the next race, each insisting his team will take the winners' podium, before Joir takes his cold leave.",
